      <title>黑暗舰队拆除是陷入困境的废墟的生命线</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/dark-fleet-demolition-is-a-lifeline-for-india-s-struggling-scrapyards</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度破旧的院子已经饿死了，而衰老的油轮则保持漂浮，以在全球范围内携带非法石油。现在，随着制裁的执法紧缩并受到单个船只的审查，有些人看到有机会扭转业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/dark-fleet-demolition-is-a-lifeline-for-india-s-struggling-scrapyards</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 02:31:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股票，比特币在酸味上下降：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对贸易伙伴的关税态度的持续转变，亚洲股票的关注率降低了，这使市场的不确定性不确定性，并掩盖了对经济前景的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 22:35:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国吹捧政策空间屏蔽经济免受贸易战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/china-signals-it-has-policy-space-to-counter-impact-of-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国最高的经济官员表示，在面对不确定性和风险的情况下，他们为国家设定了2025年的雄心勃勃的增长目标，尽管美国的关税较高，他们已经为面对不确定性和风险做出了巨大行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/china-signals-it-has-policy-space-to-counter-impact-of-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 07:55:06 GMT</pubDate>
